2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Types</h1>\n<p>The types of Slider are as follows:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Types</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Usage</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Default</td>\n<td>Shows a default Slider to select a single value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>MinRange</td>\n<td>Displays the shadow from the start value to the current selected value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Range</td>\n<td>Selects a range of values. It also displays the shadow in-between the selection range.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Both the Default Slider and Min-Range Slider have same behavior that is used to select a single value.\nIn Min-Range Slider, a shadow is considered from the start value to current handle position. But the Range Slider\ncontains two handles that is used to select a range of values and a shadow is considered in between the two handles.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> Syncfusion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EJ2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Blazor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Inputs\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"30\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"40\"</span> Type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"SliderType.MinRange\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>@<span class=\"token class-name\">RangeValue</span> Type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"SliderType.Range\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n@code<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> RangeValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">70</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/slider/images/slider-types.png\" alt=\"Blazor - Slider - Types\"></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Types The types of Slider are as follows: Types Usage Default Shows a default Slider to select a single value. MinRange Displays the shadow…","fields":{"slug":"/slider/types/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/slider/types/","previous":{"html":"<h1 id=\"customize-colorpicker\"><a href=\"#customize-colorpicker\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Customize ColorPicker</h1>\n<h2 id=\"hide-input-area-from-picker\"><a href=\"#hide-input-area-from-picker\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hide input area from picker</h2>\n<p>By default, the input area will be rendered in ColorPicker. To hide the input area from it, add <code class=\"language-text\">e-hide-value</code> class to ColorPicker using the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~CssClass.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">cssClass</code></a> property.</p>\n<p>In the following sample, the ColorPicker is rendered without input area.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">    &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n    &lt;EjsColorPicker ModeSwitcher=&quot;false&quot; CssClass=&quot;e-hide-value&quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/hide-input.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>","id":"f5586748-b037-5fcd-b4b2-c393eb981576","fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/customize-color-picker/","parentPath":"color-picker/how-to","childPath":"customize-color-picker","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"ColorPicker/How To/Customize ColorPicker","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Customize ColorPicker in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Customize ColorPicker in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"next":{"html":"<h1 id=\"tooltip\"><a href=\"#tooltip\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tooltip</h1>\n<p>The Slider displays the tooltip to indicate the current value by clicking the Slider bar or drag\nthe Slider handle. The Tooltip position can be customized by using the <code class=\"language-text\">Placement</code> property. Also decides the tooltip display mode on a page, i.e., on hovering, focusing, or clicking on the Slider handle and it always remains/displays on the page.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> Syncfusion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EJ2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Blazor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Inputs\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Min<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0\"</span> Max<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"100\"</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"30\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTooltipData</span> IsVisible<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> ShowOn<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipShowOn.Always\"</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipPlacement.After\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTooltipData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/slider/images/slider-tooltip.png\" alt=\"Blazor - Slider - Tooltip\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"buttons\"><a href=\"#buttons\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Buttons</h2>\n<p>The Slider value can be changed by using the Increase and Decrease buttons. In Range Slider, by\ndefault the first handle value will be changed while clicking the button. Change the handle focus and\npress the button to change the last focused handle value.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>After enabling the slider buttons if the ‘Tab’ key is pressed, the focus goes to the handle\nand not to the button.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> Syncfusion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EJ2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Blazor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Inputs\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EjsSlider</span> Value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"30\"</span> ShowButtons<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SliderTooltipData</span> IsVisible<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> ShowOn<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipShowOn.Always\"</span> Placement<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TooltipPlacement.After\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>SliderTooltipData<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>EjsSlider<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/slider/images/slider-buttons.png\" alt=\"Blazor - Slider - Buttons\"></p>","id":"24d8ed62-631a-5704-852a-4019d681905e","fields":{"slug":"/slider/tooltip/","parentPath":"slider","childPath":"tooltip","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Slider/Tooltip","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"Tooltip in Blazor [Preview] Slider component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Tooltip in Blazor [Preview] Slider component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Slider/Types","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"Types in Blazor [Preview] Slider component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Types in Blazor [Preview] Slider component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}}